									"numinlets" : 1,
									"numoutlets" : 0,
									"patching_rect" : [ 76.0, 654.0, 513.0, 79.0 ],
									"saved_attribute_attributes" : 									{
										"textcolor" : 										{
											"expression" : "themecolor.theme_textcolor"
										}

									}
,
									"text" : "Since this is a somewhat abstract idea, I've done my best to apply what is perceptually meaningful (where possible) changes to the material as it is delayed and decayed. This is different for each descriptor type, and is more effective in some than others. On the normal descriptors (i.e. dk.descriptors~) and melbands the results are perceptual and quite effective. With MFCCs, given their abstract nature, this is less the case."
								}

							}
, 							{
